unit1 $HOME/challenge/unit1に移動してみよう
```
cd unit1
ls
cat answer1.txt
```

unit2 $HOME/challenge/unit2でanswer2.txtを作成してみよう
```
cd unit2
touch answer2.txt
cat answer2.txt
```

unit3 $HOME/challenge/unit3からcd jp/hogera/../fuga/../../en/foo/barを実行した後カレントディレクトリを確認して
```
cd unit3
cd jp/hogera/../fuga/../../en/foo/bar
pwd
ls
cat answer3.txt
```

unit4 $HOME/challenge/unit4でanswer4.txt.tmpをanswer4.txtに名前を変更しよう
```
cd unit4
mv answer4.txt.tmp answer4.txt
cat answer4.txt
```

unit5 $HOME/challenge/unit5でanswerディレクトリを作成しよう
```
cd unit5
mkdir answer
cd answer
ls
cat answer5.txt
```

unit6 $HOME/challenge/unit6でテキストエディタを使ってdate.txtに今日の日付をYYYY/MM/DD形式で書いてみよう
```
cd unit6
vim date.txt
2023/08/05
:wq
ls
cat answer6.txt
```

unit7 $HOME/challenge/unit7のcolors.txtからanswer7.txtのパスを探そう
```
cd unit7
less colors.txt
/unit
q
cd ../unit3/jp/hoge/hogehoge
ls
cat answer7.txt
```

unit8 answer8.txtを探して
```
cd unit8
find -name answer8.txt
cd 2023/8/5
ls
cat answer8.txt
```

unit9 answer9.txtを消そう
```
cd unit9
rm answer9.txt
ls
cat answer9.txt
```

unit10 $HOME/challenge/unit10/tmp/*.tmpを消してtmpを消す
```
cd unit10
rm tmp/*tmp
rmdir tmp
ls
cat answer10.txt
```

unit11 $HOME/challenge/unit8/2022/7/2から相対パスで$HOME/challenge/unit11/answerに移動しよう
```
cd unit8/2022/7/2
cd ../../../../unit11/answer
ls 
cat answer11.txt
```

unit12 $HOME/challenge/unit12/answer12.txtを開こう
```
cd unit12
ls
cat answer12.txt
sudo cat asnwer12.txt
```

unit13 $HOME/challenge/unit13/answer13.txtのタイムスタンプを2023/8/4 14:00:00に変更してみよう
```
cd unit13
ls
cat hint.txt
touch -t 202308041400.00 answer13.txt
cat answer13.txt
```

unit14 $HOME/challenge/unit14でanswerディレクトリを作ってanswer1.txt, answer2.txt, answer3.txt, answer4.txtをanswerにコピーしてanswer14.txtを作成
```
cd unit14
mkdir answer
cd answer
cp ../../unit1/answer1.txt ./
cp ../../unit2/answer2.txt ./
cp ../../unit3/en/foo/bar/answer3.txt ./
cp ../../unit4/answer4.txt ./
touch answer14.txt
cat answer14.txt
```
